code: /**  * Case-insensitive from string method.  *  * @param value  *            String representation  * @return The condition type  */ public static Level fromString(String value) {     return Level.valueOf(value.toUpperCase(Locale.ROOT)). }
public static Level readFromStream(StreamInput in) throws IOException {     return in.readEnum(Level.class). }
@Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     out.writeEnum(this). }
